"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    The number of hemodialysis treatments per week required to obtain a particular average concentration of BUN in hypercatabolic patients with acute renal failure varies with patient weight (x axis). A, B, and C are the three curves associated with target BUN levels of 100, 80, and 60 mg/dL, respectively.",
